Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715}And now I'd like to ask Akimoto-sensei to lead the toast on behalf of all the authors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it frustrating that {\i1}KIYOSHI Knight{\i0} didn't win?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I should accept the result gracefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought your one-shot for the Tezuka Award was superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki Kou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki Yuriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like my music?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like most of your lyrics, but not the melodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to be straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you like me as a manga author?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sad face is lovely too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to turn it into a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather you turn it into a manga than a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:01:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That chief editor is pretty good, setting all this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm answering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got third place in initial polls!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a rank like that, you can just go with the first storyline you made for chapter four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, should we really be satisfied with third place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't a first chapter usually get first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you got third in {\i1}Jack{\i0}, the top shounen magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hiramaru's {\i1}Otter 11{\i0}, which started two volumes before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got first place with its first chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, {\i1}Otter{\i0} had a great start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His second chapter got third place, and his third chapter got fourth place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arai-sensei's {\i1}Baked Cheese{\i0} started last week,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the first chapter got third place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd his second chapter do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, we can expect {\i1}TRAP {\i0}'s ranking to fall that much for the second chapter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the second chapter stays in the top ten, that's an accomplishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, {\i1}TRAP {\i0}'s second and third chapters are well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a downer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some confidence in your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll tell us the rest at Friday's meeting, he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a good result, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we lost the best chance to claim the top spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko, I thought you'd be disappointed getting third but you seem fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get higher results.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm more relieved that the ranking isn't worse than it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we're aiming for the top spot with a long-running serialization, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And next up is the decisive second chapter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we don't fall as much as {\i1}Cheese{\i0} did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miura is a bit too optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's brace ourselves for now. We can't expect to get any higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're still in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the deadline for chapter four is Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pen-in as much as I can and get it ready for the assistants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko, you're calm about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in rushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho said it was good in an e-mail, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you guys get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any work to do here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, sorry for barging in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the first e-mail she's sent me since the photo book thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The second chapter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real fight is coming up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I'll reply first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Detective TRAP{\i0} got a pretty good start, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, your style suits us much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than {\i1}Shounen{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Aoki meeting with the head editor of Jack SQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing an original work with KOOGY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay, Aida?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you her editor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A while ago, I asked her to polish up {\i1}hideout door{\i0} in preparation for the next serialization meeting, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The editorial department thinks the characters need to fight against something, shounen-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are already psychological struggles in the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not exactly what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want punching and kicking, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, to put it simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave the drawing to Nakai, it'll work out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to change the content of the plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't think my story is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not willing to be flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Chief Editor Ibaraki of Jack SQ invited her to come over to his magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?! Are you for real, Yuujirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Aoki's gonna start a serialization together with KOOGY.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chief editor of Jack SQ secretly introduced them at the New Year's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, Aoki is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the deal has gone that far, she's probably not against it—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell my story to the readers no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My story isn't the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki, it's me, Nakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just speak from out here, so please listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true you're pairing up with KOOGY... no, Makaino?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? {\i1}hideout door{\i0} is a wonderful work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you submit it to the next serialization committee, it'll definitely pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your art can't convey my worldview or my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My art...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw so that it definitely satisfies you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll depict the world of Aoki Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Niizuma's assistant, so you can't take the time to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll practice without sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that as many times as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a park behind this apartment complex, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm done with work, I'll sit there and draw every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to see me from your window!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use every free moment to draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it. You're disturbing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I can draw art that satisfies you, I'll never stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless trying to convince a girl that drops you when she gets a taste of fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how much he risked on {\i1}hideout door{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai, didn't you leave for the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just came back to get my supplies and the storyline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you talk to Miss Aoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I'll want a flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to draw at Aoki's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until she's satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her place... you mean in her apartment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in her apartment. Outside of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this cold weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About manga, surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the fourth chapter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first chapter got third place in the final results too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're off to a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are third in {\i1}Jack{\i0} ! Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just hoping we don't drop with the second chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are real downers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be happy you're in third place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's aim for long-term serialization!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, speaking of serialization...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KOOGY's started serializing with Jack SQ, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KOOGY?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more, he's partnering with Aoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, he called for a press conference...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's announced, there'll be a big fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with Jack SQ,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the top of the manga world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki and KOOGY?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a different publication, so it's really got nothing to do with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Nakai know already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko, let's try calling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should we say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's try probing Fukuda for info first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin!! Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him that their first chapter was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}TRAP {\i0}'s serialization started!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma said to tell you it was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, there's something we're a bit concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Nakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard that Aoki was partnering up with KOOGY...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you guys should worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that, just focus on your serialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he told us not to worry, I'm even more worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I also think Nakai really likes Aoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Nakai can deal with a shock like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so worried about it, I can't concentrate on writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think what Fukuda said is right. Being serialized is tougher than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we just have to move forward as best we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're worried, why not just call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't concentrate on your work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda, it's Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um, is Nakai okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh fine, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the past four days, every moment he hasn't been working,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai's been drawing in the park in front of Miss Aoki's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... I don't really get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's drawing the manuscript at night where she can see him from her window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's February!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless! His hands will be frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get Miss Aoki back, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just seems like a stalker to me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betting my future as a manga author on this work of Aoki's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't work, I'll be an assistant for life, or I'll go back home to my folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is he still drawing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already past midnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be inconvenienced if you freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind and body are on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you've been watching me. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to work with you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely draw art that you can approve of!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to draw your world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to drag him back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but after seeing him, I don't have the heart to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he dies like this, he'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even if he dies"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dies!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda, I get even more worried when you use words like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to quit worrying and focus on your serialization!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nakai is going to back to Aoki's place today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably. He's entrenched himself there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I shouldn't have asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just worry about him all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to finish up the manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, she's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this Aoki person really didn't want him there, she'd call the police and they'd make him leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, she could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, should I contact the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, Nakai would curse you for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then, this woman doesn't call the police because she doesn't want him to hate her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno... maybe she's just testing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in her heart, she still has doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch it with your filthy hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, did you just call me filthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to touch my manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're way more filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just spare my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, this guy creeps me out.{not that he looks gross, but gives off an unpleasant feeeling to them}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave him and go have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could just peek inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that cold park, he drew something so perfectly..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our second chapter's in publication.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think the polls will say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've done all that we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to wait for the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's more important to pen-in the fifth chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crazy out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already starting to pile up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, the weather report said there'd be a snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowstorm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda, where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Niizuma's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm writing my own manga's plot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nakai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the park, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing pretty heavily here. How is it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's really coming down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's drawing manga in this snow, he'll die for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I had backup, I probably couldn't budge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai wants to prove he's a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it before, but this is an ambition he'll die for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his decisi—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda! What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai is a member of your Fukuda team!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cant take this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him go home, by force if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in Mitaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get to the train station, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you draw in this weather, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freezing to death for that cold-hearted woman doesn't even make for a good joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betting everything on {\i1}hideout door{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that Aoki isn't bending or changing her opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may seem cold to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think with what I draw, I can turn it around into something with passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda, we're at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of the ticket gate. {more like turnstile}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll come get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashirogi ran here because they're worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful, but it's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to work with you once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll draw so that it definitely satisfies you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll depict your world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snow's getting thicker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he'll really be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is he going to such lengths?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's just because he likes Aoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's more than just liking her, he's also in love with her work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his passion for manga is what's motivating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if he's got passion, if he hurts himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai's my buddy in the Fukuda team!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely take him home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda? I already told you I won't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this park—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your art that was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't want to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was running from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write a story that'll be worthy of your art.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My art wasn't strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it? Guess there wasn't any point in you coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in and warm yourself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? C-Can I really, really come in-into... {this is a really broken sentence, he doesnt even finish the words}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just too creepy! I take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I only invited you in just as a working partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like our rival came back with a power-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm so sorry! So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Aoki to do her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Aoki Kou couldn't become the person who understood me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be a genius really is to be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, KOOGY will draw by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, Nakai got a fever and couldn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda complained that he had trouble getting him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But now we can concentrate on {\i1}TRAP{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are the results for the second chapter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eighth?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our decisive second chapter...{shoubu as an adj...the decisive chapter, the chapter we wage battle with, the chapter of challenge, the chapter that's the real test....}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got eighth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our decisive second chapter got eighth place. {same deal as above}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will our next rank be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should support each other and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take it slow! No hurry, no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You support yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Bakuman:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.73,0:24:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Support and Patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.79,0:24:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've begun to turn our dreams to reality!
