Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:28.56,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The fight doesn't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:34.82,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder how far I've come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:40.12,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In ten years, I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:46.62,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the scenario I wrote for myself, so I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:53.25,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:59.59,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,751)\be1}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:08.31,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:14.57,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I fuel my passion until I succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:21.32,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There will be meetings and partings along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:27.58,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I'll simply believe in my strength that you've taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:33.46,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And rise back up again and again and again
